  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Erich Durrandon<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Sailmaker</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nErich Durrandon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nErich the Sailmaker</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nSon of <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Fair)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Fair)\">Durran the Fair</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Erich_Durrandon\" title=\"Erich Durrandon\">Erich Durrandon</a>.</div>\n<p><b>Erich Durrandon</b>, also known as <b>Erich the Sailmaker</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erich_Durrandon_(the_Sailmaker)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Erich was the first to claim <a href=\"/index.php/Estermont\" title=\"Estermont\">Estermont</a> and the lesser isles farther south for the Kingdom of the Storm. Scholars speculate he was most likely <b>Erich III</b>. He was the grandson of King <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Fair)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Fair)\">Durran the Fair</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erich_Durrandon_(the_Sailmaker)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Edwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Edwyn Tarth\">Edwyn<br />Tarth</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;heigh